NEWSLETTTER FOR WINDOWS 3.0 INDUSTRY

CompuThink Inc. (Bellevue, WA) has begun the publication of
"The Windows Watcher" newsletter with an issue this month.
The new monthly will follow technical developments within
the Windows 3.0 industry. It will also include user tips. A
subscription costs $39.




