LEGAL NEWSLETTER AMERICAN BAR ASSOCIATION

The American Bar Association (Chicago) has begun the
publication of "Leadership & Management Directions"

newsletter. The new monthly focuses on trends, principles,
and practices in the law practice management field.
Editorial includes analyses, briefs, reviews and event
schedules.




