NEW PUB FOR GREEN BUSINESS STRATEGIES

Carl Frankel and Molly Barnes, in affiliation with FIND/SVP
(New York) has begun the publication of "Green Market
Alert" newsletter. The publication includes marketing,
research and other resource information "for companies
seeking to learn more about green consumerism or to
implement green business strategies." The NL is an
outgrowth of FIND/SVP's "The Green Consumer" report,
released last spring. A subscription costs $395.




