EXECUTIVE FAX LETTER FROM KINGSWOOD COMMUNICATIONS

Kingswood Communciations (Lynden, WA) has begun the
publication of "The Ogden Fax Letter," a weekly two-page
fax targeted to "top executives" and corporate planners.
Editorial includes the latest developments in business,
communications, technolgy and social change "around the
world."




