BUYER SOUGHT FOR "WASHINGTON CEO" MAGAZINE

WTD, Inc. (Portland, OR) is seeking a buyer for "Washington
CEO" magazine (Seattle, WA). The monthly began publication
last December and is targeted to corporate executives in
the state of Washington. The company said that the
publication has a controlled circulation of 20,000 and that
it grossed $700,000 during its first 12 months.




