THE BUSINESS PUBLISHER via NewsNet
December 15, 1990

LOTUS AND SIMON & SCHUSTER ENTER INTO PUBLISHING DEAL

Lotus Publishing Corp. (Cambridge, MA) and Brady Books, a
unit of Simon & Schuster Professional Information Group
(New York), have entered into a book publishing agreement.
Under the deal, Brady will produce and market Lotus Books,
including four series: "Start Here" for first-time Lotus
software users, "Concise Guides" for experienced users,
"Business Solutions" for managers, and "Technical
Reference" for corporate and commercial developers.





